# Isolated agent worktrees (test harness etc.) — never part of the repo.
.claude/worktrees/

# Skill activation is per-session and LOCAL — design proposal v2 §B6.
# Only the always-on "system" skills are committed; any skill activated ad-hoc for
# one task lands in .claude/skills/ locally but must NOT leak to other branches or
# main. The whitelist below IS the always-on baseline (v3: this whitelist alone
# defines "always-on" — no policy frontmatter field); to promote a new skill to
# always-on, add a "!" line here (a deliberate, rare edit).

.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/project-memory/
!.claude/skills/checkpoint/
!.claude/skills/ship-now/
